Demon Wulf/Flesh Ripper/Dark Claw:




Demon Wulf's internal scanners detected Reptilica.  "We have a visitor near."

"Should we kill him, brother?" Flesh Ripper said, the hyena, looking around.  

"No.  We don't have current information on what is happening on this pitiful 
world." Dark Claw commented.

"True, my brothers.  We shall meet, and see if this Cybertronian is of any 
use to our cause."
